thread.title_full: JB Prince Company reviewed by Zachary

author: Zachary
title: Zachary
text: Great service no issues in delivery. Would go 4 and a half stars of possible, only issue was during initial order (from mobile device) the site crashed several times. Were i not persistent i would have changed online venues, i almost did 3 times, but worked out. And the products were fantastic, prices more than fair for the most part, delivery was right when expected.
